---
import { Section, Link, Div, H1, H2, Paragraph } from "@components/base";
import { ProfileImage, ListView, ListViewItem, ListViewItemImage, ListViewItemTitle, ListViewItemMeta, ListViewItemChevron, ListViewItemLink } from "@components/common";
import { Layout } from "@layouts";
import { getSectionCollection } from "@utils/getSectionCollection";

const experienceSection = await getSectionCollection("experience");
const mentorshipSection = await getSectionCollection("mentorship");
const projectsSection = await getSectionCollection("projects");  
const achievementsSection = await getSectionCollection("achievements");
const educationSection = await getSectionCollection("education");
---

<Layout
  title="Jonathon Toon | Home"
  description="Jonathon Toon is a software designer, leader, and mentor, living and working remotely in Aotearoa New Zealand. He has a passion for creating impactful digital experiences and fostering innovation in teams."
  keywords="design, software, product, fractional, leadership, new zealand, aoteoroa, technology, typescript, start ups, engineering, mentorship, coaching, adplist"
  twitterHandle="@jonathontoon"
  canonicalUrl="https://www.jonathontoon.com/"
  ogImage="/images/og-image.png"
>
  <Section class="flex flex-row">
    <Div class="px-2">
      <Link href="/" class="block w-24">
        <ProfileImage class="w-full aspect-square bg-blue-500 rounded-xl" />
      </Link>
    </Div>
  </Section>
  <Section class="flex flex-col gap-y-2">
    <H1 class="font-semibold text-2xl tracking-tight px-1">Nice to meet you, I'm Jonathon.</H1>
    <Paragraph class="text-stone-700 px-1">A versatile software designer, leader, and mentor, living and working remotely in Aotearoa New Zealand.</Paragraph>
    <Paragraph class="text-stone-700 indent-4 px-1">For the past 15 years, I’ve worked across the organizational stack cultivating and leading teams, while designing and shipping products at innovative companies in Asia, Oceania, and North America.</Paragraph>
    <Paragraph class="text-stone-700 indent-4 px-1">In that time, I’ve built deep, hands-on expertise in product, brand and engineering, and learned how to bring those disciplines together to create products that make a real impact.</Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section class="flex flex-col gap-y-2">
    <H2 class="font-semibold text-xl tracking-normal px-1">Experience</H2>
    <ListView>
      {experienceSection.map((experience) => (
        <ListViewItem href={experience.slug ? `/experience/${experience.slug}` : undefined}>
          <ListViewItemImage 
            slot="image" 
            src={experience.logo ? `/${experience.logo}` : undefined}
            alt={`${experience.title} logo`}
          />
          <Fragment slot="content">
            <ListViewItemTitle>{experience.title}</ListViewItemTitle>
            <ListViewItemMeta class="text-stone-700 md:hidden">{experience.subtitle}</ListViewItemMeta>
            <ListViewItemMeta class="text-stone-500 text-sm md:hidden">{experience.date}</ListViewItemMeta>
            <ListViewItemMeta class="text-stone-500 hidden md:block">{`${experience.subtitle} · ${experience.date}`}</ListViewItemMeta>
          </Fragment>
          <ListViewItemChevron slot="action" />
        </ListViewItem>
      ))}
    </ListView>
  </Section>
  <Section class="flex flex-col gap-y-2">
    <H2 class="font-semibold text-xl tracking-normal px-1">Mentorship</H2>
    <Paragraph class="text-stone-700 px-1 pb-2">Through both one-off and recurring sessions I help designers, product people and founders navigate challenges through practical, honest, actionable mentorship.</Paragraph>
    <ListView>
      {mentorshipSection.map((mentorship) => (
        <ListViewItem>
          <ListViewItemImage 
            slot="image" 
            src={mentorship.logo ? `/${mentorship.logo}` : undefined}
            alt={`${mentorship.title} logo`}
          />
          <Fragment slot="content">
            <ListViewItemTitle>{mentorship.title}</ListViewItemTitle>
            <ListViewItemMeta class="text-stone-700 md:hidden">{mentorship.subtitle}</ListViewItemMeta>
            <ListViewItemMeta class="text-stone-500 text-sm md:hidden">{mentorship.date}</ListViewItemMeta>
            <ListViewItemMeta class="text-stone-500 hidden md:block">{`${mentorship.subtitle} · ${mentorship.date}`}</ListViewItemMeta>
          </Fragment>
          {mentorship.url && (
            <ListViewItemLink href={mentorship.url} target="_blank" slot="action">
              {mentorship.urlText}
            </ListViewItemLink>
          )}
        </ListViewItem>
      ))}
    </ListView>
  </Section>
  <Section class="flex flex-col gap-y-2">
    <H2 class="font-semibold text-xl tracking-normal px-1">Projects</H2>
    <Paragraph class="text-stone-700 px-1 pb-2">I love to build things on my own. Either to explore new technologies, to make a little pocket money, or simply just for fun.</Paragraph>
    <ListView>
      {projectsSection.map((project) => (
        <ListViewItem>
          <ListViewItemImage 
            slot="image" 
            src={project.logo ? `/${project.logo}` : undefined}
            alt={`${project.title} logo`}
          />
          <Fragment slot="content">
            <ListViewItemTitle>{project.title}</ListViewItemTitle>
            <ListViewItemMeta class="text-stone-700 md:hidden">{project.subtitle}</ListViewItemMeta>
            <ListViewItemMeta class="text-stone-500 text-sm md:hidden">{project.date}</ListViewItemMeta>
            <ListViewItemMeta class="text-stone-500 hidden md:block">{`${project.subtitle} · ${project.date}`}</ListViewItemMeta>
          </Fragment>
          {project.url && (
            <ListViewItemLink href={project.url} target="_blank" slot="action">
              {project.urlText}
            </ListViewItemLink>
          )}
        </ListViewItem>
      ))}
    </ListView>
  </Section>
  <Section class="flex flex-col gap-y-2">
    <H2 class="font-semibold text-xl tracking-normal px-1">Patents, Publications, Awards</H2>
    <Paragraph class="text-stone-700 px-1 pb-2">Highlights from my career and education which have been picked up in the press, recognized with awards, or even patented.</Paragraph>
    <ListView>
      {achievementsSection.map((achievement) => (
        <ListViewItem>
          <ListViewItemImage 
            slot="image" 
            src={achievement.logo ? `/${achievement.logo}` : undefined}
            alt={`${achievement.title} logo`}
          />
          <Fragment slot="content">
            <ListViewItemTitle>{achievement.title}</ListViewItemTitle>
            <ListViewItemMeta class="text-stone-700 md:hidden">{achievement.subtitle}</ListViewItemMeta>
            <ListViewItemMeta class="text-stone-500 text-sm md:hidden">{achievement.date}</ListViewItemMeta>
            <ListViewItemMeta class="text-stone-500 hidden md:block">{`${achievement.subtitle} · ${achievement.date}`}</ListViewItemMeta>
          </Fragment>
          {achievement.url && (
            <ListViewItemLink href={achievement.url} target="_blank" slot="action">
              {achievement.urlText}
            </ListViewItemLink>
          )}
        </ListViewItem>
      ))}
    </ListView>
  </Section>
  <Section class="flex flex-col gap-y-2">
    <H2 class="font-semibold text-xl tracking-normal px-1">Education</H2>
    <ListView>
      {educationSection.map((education) => (
        <ListViewItem>
          <ListViewItemImage 
            slot="image" 
            src={education.logo ? `/${education.logo}` : undefined}
            alt={`${education.title} logo`}
          />
          <Fragment slot="content">
            <ListViewItemTitle>{education.title}</ListViewItemTitle>
            <ListViewItemMeta class="text-stone-700 md:hidden">{education.subtitle}</ListViewItemMeta>
            <ListViewItemMeta class="text-stone-500 text-sm md:hidden">{education.date}</ListViewItemMeta>
            <ListViewItemMeta class="text-stone-500 hidden md:block">{`${education.subtitle} · ${education.date}`}</ListViewItemMeta>
          </Fragment>
          {education.url && (
            <ListViewItemLink href={education.url} target="_blank" slot="action">
              {education.urlText}
            </ListViewItemLink>
          )}
        </ListViewItem>
      ))}
    </ListView>
  </Section>
  <Section class="flex flex-col gap-y-2">
    <H2 class="font-semibold text-xl tracking-normal px-1">Colophon</H2>
    <Paragraph class="text-stone-700 px-1">
      Websites aren't temples, but rather as landscapes. Things which change over time. Here's a little about how I built this current iteration is built.
    </Paragraph> 
    <Paragraph class="text-stone-700 px-1 indent-4">
      All visual elements are designed by myself or their respective owners. Each page is typeset in Archivo by <Link href="https://www.omnibus-type.com/" target="">Omnibus Type</Link>. Try it yourself on <Link href="https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Archivo?query=Omnibus-Type" target="_blank">Google Fonts</Link>. The icons used are from the wonderful <Link href="https://minoradventures.lemonsqueezy.com?aff=zOG5V" target="_blank">Amicons</Link> set, by Marek Minor. Grab your own copy <Link href="https://minoradventures.lemonsqueezy.com?aff=zOG5V" target="_blank">today</Link>.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph class="text-stone-700 px-1 indent-4">
      The technology powering this website is <Link href="https://astro.build" target="_blank">Astro</Link>, a server-first framework that generates static pages. Hosting, deployment and analytics are all provided by <Link href="https://pages.cloudflare.com" target="_blank">Cloudflare</Link>.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph class="text-stone-700 px-1 indent-4">
      All meeting scheduling and video calls for mentorship sessions are handled through <Link href="https://refer.cal.com/jonathontoon" target="_blank">Cal.com</Link>, while all payments are facilitated by <Link href="https://stripe.com/" target="_blank">Stripe</Link>.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
</Layout>
